summary: Relive the journal of a twisted individual who sought refuge at the Alchemist's Shack, and seek him out before his experiments end yet another life.
descriptionHtml: This is the BETA release of "For Whom Death Tolls", a horror mod created by puppy14.  It begins and ends at the Alchemist's Shack, which is located south of Ivarstead.  It contains elements of surprise, horror, new music, interesting puzzles, and a final battle to end the mod.  This is my first attempt, and I'm certain once this is out of BETA, the description and the mod will be better.  I just want people to try it now, and offer feedback.
author: puppy14
